OL,3,CMan murdered lodger and scattered body
OL,4,Cparts around seaside town
OL,6,FA man who killed his lodger before
OL,7,Fscattering his body parts around a
OL,8,Fseaside town has been convicted of
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,F49-year old Benjamin Lee Atkins
OL,12,Ffatally attacked 49-year old Simon
OL,13,FShotton with a knife at his home in
OL,14,FBoscombe following a disagreement over
OL,15,Fmoney in August 2023.
OL,17,FOver the space of two weeks Dorset
OL,18,FPolice found human remains after they
OL,19,Fwere discovered by members of the
OL,20,Fpublic.
