OL,3,CMan murdered lodger and scattered body
OL,4,Cparts around seaside town
OL,6,FThe first discovery came on Saturday
OL,7,F26th August 2023 at the Manor Steps
OL,8,FZig Zag, off Boscombe Overcliff Drive
OL,9,Fwhere Mr Shotton's leg was found.
OL,11,FWhen detectives then discovered his
OL,12,Fphone was sold by Atkins, on Friday
OL,13,F1st September he and his partner were
OL,14,Farrested.
OL,16,F39-year old partner Debbie Ann Pereira
OL,17,Fwas found guilty of perverting the
OL,18,Fcourse of having previously admitting
OL,19,Fa charge of preventing the burial of a
OL,20,Fcorpse during the course of the trial.
