OL,3,CMan murdered lodger and scattered body
OL,4,Cparts around seaside town
OL,6,FAt the property, searches of the rear
OL,7,Fgarden led detectives to Mr Shotton's
OL,8,Farms with neighbours reporting that
OL,9,FAtkins had been burning items in his
OL,10,Fgarden in the days leading up to his
OL,11,Farrest.
OL,13,FDays later, on the 6th September 2023,
OL,14,FMr Shotton's human remains had been
OL,15,Ffound in a black suitcase in the area
OL,16,Fof Boscombe Chine Gardens, near to
OL,17,FBoscombe Pier.
