OL,6,FA post-mortem examination of Mr
OL,7,FShotton's arms and torso revealed a
OL,8,Fnumber of small puncture wounds as
OL,9,Fwell as slash type injuries that
OL,10,Fappeared to be defensive wounds trying
OL,11,Fto fend off Atkins' knife.
OL,13,FKirsty Gordon, a Senior Crown
OL,14,FProsecutor with CPS Wessex, said,
OL,15,F"This was a truly disturbing case
OL,16,Fwhich shocked the residents of
OL,17,FBournemouth and its surrounding towns.
