OL,3,CMan murdered lodger and scattered body
OL,4,Cparts around seaside town
OL,6,F"Atkins and Pereira's cruelty and lack
OL,7,Fof humanity is laid bare ` after Mr
OL,8,FShotton was murdered by Atkins in cold
OL,9,Fblood over a minor dispute, they
OL,10,Frobbed him the dignity of a proper
OL,11,Fburial.
OL,13,F"We worked closely with Dorset Police,
OL,14,Fwhose meticulous investigation work
OL,15,Fgreatly aided our ability to deliver
OL,16,Fswift justice in an incredibly complex
OL,17,Fcase where evidence continued to
OL,18,Funfold months after the defendants
OL,19,Fwere charged.
