OL,6,F"This has been an extremely complex
OL,7,Finvestigation, firstly to identify the
OL,8,Fvictim and then to compile evidence to
OL,9,Festablish the involvement of the
OL,10,Fdefendants in this case. I want to
OL,11,Fthank all those involved for their
OL,12,Ftireless efforts to ensure we were
OL,13,Fable to secure justice for Mr
OL,14,FShotton's family.
OL,16,F"I also want to thank the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service for its support in
OL,18,Fbringing this case to trial and
OL,19,Fsecuring the convictions of these
OL,20,Fdefendants."
